P5+1 Nuclear Negotiations With Iran


Secretary Kerry (June 27): "We have a lot of hard work to do. We have some very tough issues, and I think we all look forward to getting down to the final effort here to see whether or not a deal is possible." Full Text» Trip Page»





American Engagement and Leadership


Deputy Secretary Blinken (June 26): "Our leadership is producing powerful and positive results -- helping speed the winds of progress and temper some of the gales of turmoil." Full Text» Video»





Release of the 2014 Country Reports on Human Rights Practices


Secretary Kerry (June 25): "The message at the heart of these reports is that countries do best when their citizens fully enjoy the rights and freedoms to which they are entitled." Full Text» Reports» Briefing» Media Note» DipNote»






